What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Remember that the senior essay is actually only one class, don't pull your teeth out over it. I had a good time, but I felt like I had already done my "senior essay" life-altering work in other classes junior year.
FIND A GOOD ADVISOR!! I didn't and it sucked.
Writing a Humanities senior thesis is great because you can do what you want but the DUS doesn't really give you guidelines for anything so it feels a little uncomfortable.
Do the year long essay! Make it the focus of your senior year! Pick a good advisor. You will not regret it.
